results.question: Which questions have the most answers?
results.query_used:
MATCH (q:Question)-[:HAS_ANSWER]->(a:Answer) 
WITH q, count(a) as answer_count 
ORDER BY answer_count DESC 
RETURN q.question_id, answer_count LIMIT 10

results.question: What questions mention 'user' in their title or body?
results.query_used: MATCH (q:Question) WHERE q.title CONTAINS 'user' OR q.body CONTAINS 'user' RETURN q.question_id, q.title

results.question: What questions are tagged with user-behavior?
Which user has asked the most questions?
results.query_used: MATCH (u:User)-[:ASKED]->(q:Question) WITH u, count(q) as question_count ORDER BY question_count DESC LIMIT 1 RETURN u.display_name, question_count

results.question: Which users have both asked questions and provided answers?
results.query_used: MATCH (u:User) WHERE EXISTS((u)-[:ASKED]->(:Question)) AND EXISTS((u)-[:ANSWERED]->(:Answer)) RETURN DISTINCT u.display_name, u.user_id
